Create a premium cinematic landing page for an organic henna cone brand called “Leafy_lure”.

The website aesthetic should feel like a luxury organic beauty/skincare brand mixed with traditional mehndi artistry. The design must be elegant, minimal, smooth, immersive, and modern — not flashy ecommerce style.

Use:

* Beige, olive green, dark brown, matte black, and soft gold accents
* Soft organic gradients
* Minimal typography
* Smooth animations
* Premium spacing and layout

The website should include these sections and interactions:

---

HERO SECTION (MOST IMPORTANT)

Create a fullscreen cinematic hero section.

Background:

* Soft beige/earthy gradient background
* Tiny floating henna leaves moving slowly across the screen
* Leaves should have natural wind-like motion
* Add depth/parallax to the leaves

Main Animation:

* Initially the screen is filled with moving organic leaves
* As the page loads, the leaves gather and slowly reveal a premium 3D henna cone in the center
* The cone should float gently and rotate slightly
* Add subtle lighting and shadow for realistic premium feel

Mouse Interaction:

* Leaves slightly react to cursor movement
* Cone rotates slightly based on mouse movement
* Add soft glow/light follow effect near cursor

Hero Content:
Large luxury typography:
“Leafy_lure”

Tagline:
“Pure Organic Henna Crafted Naturally”

Buttons:

* Shop Now
* Explore Designs

Buttons should have:

* Glassmorphism or soft matte style
* Smooth hover animations

Hero section should feel cinematic like Apple or luxury skincare websites.

Use GSAP-style scroll animations and smooth transitions throughout the site.

---

SECTION 2 — PRODUCT BENEFITS

Create a clean modern section showcasing product features.

Include animated cards or icons for:

* 100% Organic
* Chemical Free
* Dark Natural Stain
* Smooth Application
* Skin Friendly

Use soft fade-up animations on scroll.
Add subtle moving leaf particles in background.

---

SECTION 3 — INGREDIENTS / NATURAL STORY

Create a storytelling section showing:

* Henna leaves
* Natural ingredients
* Organic preparation feel

Use layered parallax scrolling and cinematic transitions.

Add elegant text blocks explaining:

* Organic ingredients
* Natural dark stain
* Handmade quality

Use earthy visuals and smooth reveal animations.

---

SECTION 4 — MEHNDI GALLERY

Create a premium gallery section with beautiful mehndi-on-hand photography.

Layout:

* Masonry grid
* Hover zoom effects
* Smooth fade-in on scroll

The gallery should feel luxurious and Instagram-worthy.

---

SECTION 5 — CALL TO ACTION

Large centered section with elegant typography.

Text:
“Bring Nature to Your Art”

Add premium animated button:
“Shop Leafy_lure”

Background:

* Soft animated mehndi patterns
* Floating particles
* Subtle lighting

---

GLOBAL WEBSITE REQUIREMENTS

* Smooth scrolling
* Premium cinematic transitions
* Minimal luxury aesthetic
* Organic beauty brand feel
* Responsive design for mobile and desktop
* Modern UI/UX
* High-end product presentation

Animation Style:

* Smooth
* Slow
* Elegant
* Premium
* Natural

Avoid:

* Bright flashy colors
* Overcrowded UI
* Cheap ecommerce appearance
* Harsh animations

Inspiration style:
Apple product pages, luxury skincare brands, organic beauty brands, cinematic scroll storytelling websites.
